{"tid":754994,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《死侍2》導演有望翻拍李小龍《龍爭虎鬥》","createTime":"2018-07-25T00:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T12:55:28.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9e659b74d4807cb664266d29caebfafba1ab0abb","tid":754994,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:29:01.000Z","msg":"已故武打巨星李小龍主演電影《龍爭虎鬥》將被翻拍，據網站《Deadline》報道，電影籌備仍然喺初步階段，華納電影公司正斟洽《死侍2》（Deadpool 2）導演David Leitch執導，編劇同主要演員仍然在物色當中。<br />\n<br />\n《龍爭虎鬥》於1973年7月26日在香港上映，主角李小龍卻在該片公映前六日離世，令影迷極度悲痛。《龍爭虎鬥》過去多次傳來翻拍消息，但最終都唔成事，電影除李小龍外，還有石堅、洪金寶、成龍、元華及元彪參與演出，被譽為最偉大嘅武打片之一，美國國會圖書館於2004年將該作品放入美國國家電影資料館收藏，讚《龍爭虎鬥》「極具文化、歷史意義」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180724/58480011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58480011&d=%2B7Pt3pkRVvoFF7tiJgRHYMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7e5d7fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F58480011&h=b51fe928\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180724/58480011</a>"},{"pid":"aa0134407fa68a442404a4caadb531bf436fa898","tid":754994,"uid":186784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"扮李小龍既冇可能唔係陳國坤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff6cb340d666d9b2fa2e154922b2c207df62fca","tid":754994,"uid":135313,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:12:04.000Z","msg":"搵伍允龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6c1c8aeea8f3934595ce499d70f31db25f5c18","tid":754994,"uid":16092,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0134407fa68a442404a4caadb531bf436fa898","tid":754994,"uid":186784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"扮李小龍既冇